text: Carneades nigrosignata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Per Olof Christopher Aurivillius in 1926. It is known from Bolivia.BioLib.cz - Carneades nigrosignata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Colobotheini Category:Beetles described in 1926
